plot outline: 'Ollie Klublershturf vs. The Nazis' is an off-the-wall comedy set around the dinner table. What at first glance seems like an awkward 'meet the parents' situation for Dade Klublershturf quickly turns into a game of cat and mouse between Nazis, his boy genius younger brother, Ollie, and a time machine (disguised as an Atari joy stick) the Nazis are trying to capture from him...
title: Ollie Klublershturf vs. the Nazis
